Beautiful Game! Run's smoothly, community based game where the developer actually listen and adds suggestions the community talk about.

Custom Moose Skins made by the community is such an amazing feature! #GreatGame #WorthIt

I've supported the developer all the way till now and I will continue to do so, I am happy this has been released on steam as you too will be able to witness the greatest I am witnessing! <3

reviewText:
Early Access Review

OMG this game! So freaking funny. Nothing else matters, I haven't eaten in a weeks. My girlfriend left me yesterday..but it's worth it! The strongest point of this game is that you can test your level even if you friends is building it. There is no limit on the map size. I really like the funny atmosphere. Go talk to Suspicious Moose and he will give you the tools to edit the map. You can use your own custom skin in-game (Mine was my friend's head).

Absolutely recommended!
1000 / 10 IGN

reviewText: Early Access Review\n\nTried playing it with my friend. Wasn't worth the money at all. Maybe this game will go somewhere eventually, and I hope so, but right now there's really no instruction on what to do and seems pretty pointless. And I don't mean pointless as in you just do random stuff. I mean as in literally there seems to be nothing to do. I would not recommend spending money on it at this point.
